CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 12, 1966, pg. 1B reads: "Attractive Trio - Don't know what was said, but Mr. and Mrs. Joseph L. Barrow and Mrs. Dennis M. Stroud seem to be enjoying themselves. The attractive trio got together during intermission at the Kappa Silhouettes Black White Ball."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Joseph L. Barrow and Mrs. Dennis M. Stroud, posed in Penn Sheraton Hotel for Kappa Alpha Psi Silhouettes Black and White Ball
